---
title: Moroccan Chicken, Chickpea & Roast Veggie Curry  with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Enjoy the medley of fragrant flavours in this Moroccan-spiced curry with a gentle warming heat. Make it a low fuss
meal that doesn't sacrifice on flavour with chickpeas and chicken chunks that add a moreish bite when added to the creamy
roast veggie curry sauce.
